# Biome & Style Rule

## Purpose

Guarantee every commit passes the shared `biome.json`.

## Trigger

On file creation _or_ save of `.ts`, `.tsx`, `.js`, `.jsx`.

## Must-Pass Rules (high-level)

```bash
bun run biome:check
bun run biome:lint
bun run biome:format
bun run biome:ci
```

## Auto-Fix

| Violation                        | Fix                                                  |
| -------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| Missing arrow-fn component       | Convert to `const X: FC = () => {}`.                 |
| Unused import                    | Remove it.                                           |
| `console.log`                    | Replace with `console.warn` (or delete).             |
| Inline `style=` in JSX           | Suggest `sx` prop (MUI) or styled-component wrapper. |
| Type-only import used at runtime | Rewrite to `import type`.                            |

**Post-generation hook:** After Cursor creates or edits files, automatically run

```bash
bun run biome:lint
bun run biome:format
```

so the touched files are formatted and lint-errors are auto-corrected.

